; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the recompute path after fixated cost resolution where
; balanced virtual postings ([Account]) are skipped.
; The fixated price {=$1.10} triggers the recompute, and the
; balanced virtual postings are excluded from the balance recalculation.

2024/03/01 Fixated with balanced virtual
    Assets:EUR        100 EUR {=$1.10}
    Assets:Checking  $-110.00
    [Budget:Allocation]    $50.00
    [Budget:Reserve]      $-50.00

test bal
            $-110.00
             100 EUR  Assets
            $-110.00    Checking
             100 EUR    EUR
                   0  Budget
              $50.00    Allocation
             $-50.00    Reserve
--------------------
            $-110.00
             100 EUR
end test
